Usage: createPipelineBusGuide [-help] [-layer <id1:id2>]
                              [-netGroup <netGroupNames>] [-widthFactor <val>] [-spacing <val> [-report <fileName>]]

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
-layer <id1:id2>              # guide layers (string, optional)
-netGroup <netGroupNames>     # name(s) of net group(s) (string, optional)
-report <fileName>            # analysis report file name (string, optional)
-spacing <val>                # maximum space between flops (float, optional)
-widthFactor <val>            # guide width factor (float, optional)